  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">A Query is an input that the LightRAG framework processes, for which keywords are generated, and which is unified with multi-source text to generate answers.&lt;SEP&gt;An input question presented to the LLM, such as "What metrics are most informative for evaluating movie recommendation systems?".&lt;SEP&gt;The input question "What metrics are most informative for evaluating movie recommendation systems?" used in the retrieval and generation example.</data>
