  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Keywords extracted from a query that focus on specific entities, details, or concrete terms.&lt;SEP&gt;Specific keywords extracted from a query, such as "Accuracy", "Precision", and "Recall".&lt;SEP&gt;Keywords focusing on specific entities, details, or concrete terms.</data>
