<node id="Comprehensiveness">
  <data key="d0">Comprehensiveness</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">An evaluation dimension assessing how thoroughly an answer addresses all aspects and details of a question.&lt;SEP&gt;An evaluation metric or dimension assessing the breadth of information coverage and ability to discover relevant information.&lt;SEP&gt;Comprehensiveness is a quality demonstrating LightRAG's superiority over baseline models.&lt;SEP&gt;A criterion used in the evaluation framework to assess the detail and coverage of an answer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fef3e239f1910dc4633864fe3bf43b2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d2486b21dde7cdf31705139342854ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45c46ee88a9a2d60d923862ae51dbb45&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd4ed1717f8c1090154df49ba8cb327a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1768751026</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Diversity">
  <data key="d0">Diversity</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">An evaluation dimension assessing how varied and rich an answer is in offering different perspectives and insights.&lt;SEP&gt;An evaluation metric or dimension assessing the variety and array of information provided.&lt;SEP&gt;A characteristic of information that LightRAG aims to provide and improve through high-level retrieval; LightRAG is identified as superior in this aspect in a case study.&lt;SEP&gt;An evaluation dimension for movie recommendation systems, also a low-level keyword.&lt;SEP&gt;Diversity is a quality demonstrating LightRAG's superiority over baseline models.&lt;SEP&gt;A criterion used in the evaluation framework to assess the variety of perspectives and insights in an answer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fef3e239f1910dc4633864fe3bf43b2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d2486b21dde7cdf31705139342854ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6c67b3382f509ac5b049a984b30f29c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45c46ee88a9a2d60d923862ae51dbb45&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c80e23a4f1cc3df3c051d5673ddddb5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd4ed1717f8c1090154df49ba8cb327a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1768751026</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Empowerment">
  <data key="d0">Empowerment</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">An evaluation dimension assessing how effectively an answer enables the reader to understand the topic and make informed judgments.&lt;SEP&gt;An evaluation metric or dimension assessing the quality and impact of the content delivered.&lt;SEP&gt;A characteristic of content that LightRAG aims to deliver and enhance through low-level retrieval; LightRAG is identified as superior in this aspect in a case study.&lt;SEP&gt;Empowerment is a quality demonstrating LightRAG's superiority over baseline models.&lt;SEP&gt;A criterion used in the evaluation framework to assess how well an answer helps a reader understand and make informed judgments.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fef3e239f1910dc4633864fe3bf43b2f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d2486b21dde7cdf31705139342854ac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6c67b3382f509ac5b049a984b30f29c0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45c46ee88a9a2d60d923862ae51dbb45&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd4ed1717f8c1090154df49ba8cb327a</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1768751026</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
