<node id="Generation Component">
  <data key="d0">Generation Component</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Generation Component is an essential element of a RAG framework, responsible for taking retrieved information and generating coherent, contextually relevant responses.</data>
