</node>
<node id="Input Query">
  <data key="d0">Input Query</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">An Input Query is processed by RQ-RAG, which leverages an LLM to decompose it into multiple sub-queries.&lt;SEP&gt;An input query is the user's query provided to the Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) framework.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-69aa0eae6d1f6ab69e22f063ae2a2e46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-406bf69e556a29330cb91c63e689dffc</data>
