  <data key="d0">Indexed Data Structure (ˆD)</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Indexed Data Structure (ˆD) is a specific data structure built by the Data Indexer (φ), designed to enable rapid and cost-efficient retrieval.</data>
