  <data key="d0">Cardiologists</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Cardiologists are medical professionals who assess symptoms to identify potential heart issues, used as an example entity for extraction.&lt;SEP&gt;An example entity that can be extracted, representing medical professionals who diagnose heart disease.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-69aa0eae6d1f6ab69e22f063ae2a2e46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47f20c669a70fff5620e01924436985d</data>
