  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Entities are core components of knowledge graphs that LightRAG's vector-based search focuses on retrieving.&lt;SEP&gt;Entities are identifiable objects, concepts, or individuals mentioned in text, extracted by LightRAG.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-69aa0eae6d1f6ab69e22f063ae2a2e46&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-406bf69e556a29330cb91c63e689dffc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2c80e23a4f1cc3df3c051d5673ddddb5</data>
