<node id="Local Subgraphs">
  <data key="d0">Local Subgraphs</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Local Subgraphs are parts of the retrieved graph elements from which LightRAG gathers neighboring nodes to enhance high-order relatedness.&lt;SEP&gt;Subgraphs of retrieved graph elements within which neighboring nodes are gathered to incorporate high-order relatedness.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-47f20c669a70fff5620e01924436985d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-406bf69e556a29330cb91c63e689dffc</data>
