  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Retrieval-Augmented Generation Systems are a class of systems that LightRAG is compared against, focusing on retrieving information to augment generation.&lt;SEP&gt;Systems designed to enhance large language models by integrating external knowledge sources for more accurate and contextually relevant responses.</data>
